            <div class="technical-section__item">
                <div class="technical-section__icon">🚀</div>
                <h3 class="technical-section__item-title">Brza Aplikacija</h3>
                <p class="technical-section__item-desc">
                    Nema potrebe za degreasing i surface prep — VpCI vre&#263;ica ili film
                    se jednostavno postavi uz metal.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

